41:25.700 --> 41:28.266
- Is there any specific tea
that you enjoy?

41:28.266 --> 41:30.200
- Ginger. Lemon ginger.
- Yeah, lemon ginger?

41:30.233 --> 41:31.667
Absolutely.
I'll bring it right out to you.

41:31.700 --> 41:33.333
- Thank you so much.
- Yeah. No problem.

41:33.367 --> 41:34.467
- Matt, Matt, Lee,
when you got a second,

41:34.500 --> 41:35.533
come up to the bridge.

41:35.567 --> 41:37.000
- On my way.

41:37.033 --> 41:40.233
- Thanks, bud.
- What's up?

41:40.266 --> 41:41.567
- Hey, bud. How's it going?
- Good. Good.

41:41.567 --> 41:43.700
