41:55.567 --> 41:56.567
I'm looking for you
to get a little

41:56.600 --> 41:58.767
out of your comfort zone.

41:59.000 --> 42:00.767
I want Bruno out of the galley.

42:01.000 --> 42:04.300
I really want these next
two charters to just, like...

42:04.300 --> 42:06.266
- Well, last night was a hit.

42:06.300 --> 42:08.266
They said it was one of the
best meals they've ever had.

42:08.300 --> 42:10.000
But I will pull out
all the stops.

42:10.033 --> 42:12.166
- If we can, it'd be great.
- Absolutely.

42:12.166 --> 42:13.533
